# Changelog

## [0.3.1]
### Fixed
- (UseDataSource): fix decorator type

## [0.3.0]
### Added
- (ControlHideShowDirective): add support for ngControl injection

## [0.2.1]
### Fixed
- add ComposeOptionsTransformers

## [0.2.0]
### Added
- IsEqualToDirective

## [0.1.6]
### Fixed
- expose form directives with own modules

## [0.1.5]
### Fixed
- (InputSelectOptions): add change detection after render

## [0.1.4]
### Fixed
- (InputSelectOptions): cache the last options

## [0.1.3]
### Fixed
- (InputSelectOptions): split the options loading logic to allow extension

## [0.1.2]
### Fixed
- (InputSelectOptions): expose class members to child classes

## [0.1.1]
### Fixed
- (InputSelectOptions): allow render method extension

## [0.1.0]
### Added
- support for data source transformers

## [0.0.6]
### Fixed
- peer dependencies

## [0.0.5]
### Fixed
- use the current injection tree to create options data sources

## [0.0.4]
### Added
- ng-update support

## [0.0.3]
### Added
- add theming support

## [0.0.2]
### Added
- ControlDataSource
- ControlHideShowDirective
- InputSelectOptionsDirective
- @UseFormComponent
- ExtractDataSourceMixin
- ExtractControlMixin
- ExtrectFormDefinitionMixin

## [0.0.1]

Project initialisation
